    "description": "Double your main protein. Studded with sweet chopped dates and spring onion and oven baked for ease, these flavoursome, tender lean beef meatballs make for a deliciously exotic dinner. You'll use harissa to flavour your couscous and serve the dish with dollops of creamy yoghurt and a smattering of toasted cashew nuts.",
